description:
The fall of Lucifer is something that every human being must understand. This critical event has led to a global battle begin good and evil. Each of us is at the center of that battle, whether we realize it or not. The stakes are high - eternal life is hanging in the balance. This video will reveal how you can be victorious!

This message was preached in Manila, Philipines.
